          <caption><m>\ds \frac{\tan \theta}{2}</m> &amp; <m>\geq</m> &amp; <m>\ds \frac{\theta}{2}</m> &amp; <m>\geq</m> &amp; <m>\ds \frac{\sin \theta}{2}</m></caption>
